== UBUZIMA BWITE ==
Karekezi Claire ni inzobere (Docteur) yize iby'imikorere y'ubwonko, mukubaga ubwonko ndetse no kuvura indwara zibwibasira n'imitsi ikorana nabwo,  ni umwe muri bacye m'ubanyarwanda  wabashije kwiga kubaga ubwonko, ndetse akaba yarahawe n'ibihembo bitandukanye.

=== AMASHURI YIZE ===
Dr Karekezi Claire (w'imwaka 39 yavukiye i Butare) ariko yaje kwiga mu mujyi wa Kigali aho amashuri yisumbuye yayize muri Lycee Notr Damme de Cieaux akomereza muri Sant Andre aho yize imibare n'ubugenge (sciences) nyuma yerekeza muri Kaminuza y'u Rwanda aho yize ubuvuzi.<ref>https://inyarwanda.com/inkuru/91553/menya-byinshi-kuri-dr-claire-karekezi-umunyarwandakazi-wa-mbere-ndetse-rukumbi-ubaga-ubwon-91553.html</ref><ref>http://www.kigaliwomen.com/spip.php?article799</ref>  Dr Karekezi Claire arangije kaminuza i Butare yahisemo kujya kongera ubumenyi mu ishami ryo kubag ubwonko n'umugongo akaba yarakoreye imenyerezwa muri Sweden, ariko akomeza kwiga kwimenyereza kubaga ubwonko. nyuma akomereza imenyerezamwuga mu Kaminuza ya Oxford mu Bwongereza, nyuma akomereza amaso ye muri Marroco ahiga imyaka 5, muri 2007 yagiye kwiga andi maso muri Canada mukubaga ibibyimba by'ubwonko. Akaba yaragiye kwiga kubaga ubwonko nk'indoto yari afite. Avuga neza Ikinyarwanda, Icyongerez,Igiswahili n'Icyarabu gike.

==== IBIHEMBO ====
Numwe mu bagore bahembwe na Forbes nk'umugore w'intangarugero. Igihembo cyizwi nka Academic Excellence Award gihabwa umugore wabaye indashyikirwa mubijyanye n'amasomo ndetse n'ubumenyi, Uretse kuba umuganga m'u Rwanda uyu mugore ni umuyobozi mukuru w'ihuriro ry'abagore bo muri Afurika b'inzobere mukubaga no kuvura ubwonko.<ref>https://igihe.com/amakuru/u-rwanda/article/dr-karekezi-yegukanye-forbes-woman-africa-awards</ref>

